	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Another way to earn faction with Temple of Solusek Ro is to kill Shadowed Men.  Certainly not the easiest way, but a hell of a lot faster than turning in rings and gold/plat in South Ro.  I went into the Temple with an apprehensive con and after killing the shadowed men camp in Lavastorm a few times fonud I was finally amiable (and a low amiable at that).  The cauldron was no problem.  <BR>
<BR>
Just a note on the Shadowed Men.  They aren't all that difficult if you get one at a time, but be very careful if there are more.  I was working on faction with a 51 Palladin and we were both wiped out when six spawned on top of us.  These guys not only hit hard, but they also spawn with healer, necro, and warrior classes.  Some will have dual wield, some will have pets.  If these guys con blue to you, you'd better have a full, well-rounded group of similar levels with you.  They are a real pain in the neck.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
