	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				*EASY way to get faction quickly with the Temple of Solusek Ro*<BR>
<BR>
Go to Castle Mistmoore<BR>
<BR>
In the graveyard there is a tomb that looks like a house out of the Flinstones. Behind the tomb is a Shadowed Man named Ssynthi that worships Solusek Ro. <BR>
Speak to him and he tells you about leaving the order of the Shadowed Men and he gives you a quest.<BR>
The body of his true love is in the casket inside the tomb. On the top of the casket there is a flower.<BR>
Pick up the flower from the tomb, be sure not to step to the left or right of the casket as there are trap doors in the floor.<BR>
Give the flower to Ssynthi.<BR>
He gives positive faction with Temple of Solusek Ro, negative faction with the Shadowed Men and he gives you a Rod that is Necromancer only and has no stats...I suspect this item is used for the Wheel of Time...but that is irrelevant to my post.<BR>
The flower respawns approximately every 2 minutes.<BR>
This is FAR easier than collecting Derv rings.<BR>
Good luck.<BR>
<BR>
Kronenburg Ponykeg<BR>
Pack Elder &lt;Aegis Wolves&gt;<BR>
Master Fletcher<BR>
Master Blacksmith<BR>
Paladin of Underfoot<BR>
Tunare Server
				</font>
			</td>

